@startuml
title Siemens U273 Plugin - Scientific / Realtime Model Boundary

[*] --> GuardedBoundary

GuardedBoundary --> ScientificReferenceOffline : validation run
ScientificReferenceOffline --> GuardedBoundary : report generated

GuardedBoundary --> RealtimeApprox : build DSP tables / choose MVP mode
RealtimeApprox --> RealtimeApprox : process audio

GuardedBoundary --> HypothesisMode : user enables hypothesis
HypothesisMode --> RealtimeApprox : fallback to safe model
HypothesisMode --> GuardedBoundary : disable hypothesis

state GuardedBoundary {
  [*] --> B6Closed
  B6Closed --> B11TheveninParametric
  B11TheveninParametric --> BjtNotStamped
}

note right of ScientificReferenceOffline
May allocate and solve:
- DC
- AC
- transient
Never called by processBlock.
end note

note right of RealtimeApprox
Must be bounded and tested
against golden references.
end note

note bottom of HypothesisMode
Hypothesis must be labelled.
No hidden claim of full transistor closure.
end note

@enduml

